<lb n="0758a01" ed="T"/>低彌魚眼、婆迦利陀眼<note place="inline">已上無正名可譯</note>、鷹眼、鞞<note n="0758001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（薩）＋羅【三】</note><note n="0758001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羅【大】，薩羅【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0758001"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】 【明】">薩羅</rdg></app>眼
<lb n="0758a02" ed="T"/><note place="inline">亦無<note n="0758002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">正＝王【元】＊</note><note n="0758002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">正【大】＊，王【元】＊</note><app n="0758002"><lem wit="【大】">正</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">王</rdg></app>名</note>、<note n="0758003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">獼＝猨【三】</note><note n="0758003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">獼【大】，猨【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0758003"><lem wit="【大】">獼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】 【明】">猨</rdg></app>猴眼、狗眼、阿<note n="0758004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">荼＝茶【明】</note><note n="0758004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">荼【大】，茶【明】</note><app n="0758004"><lem wit="【大】">荼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">茶</rdg></app>迦羅眼<note place="inline">亦無<app type="star" corresp="#0758002"><lem wit="【大】">正</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">王</rdg></app>名</note>、薩多
<lb n="0758a03" ed="T"/>泥去多眼、尸陵伽羅眼<note place="inline">義云角</note>、汗眼、黃眼、刪由迦
<lb n="0758a04" ed="T"/>多眼、娑賀賀那眼、缺眼、雉眼、瞿利多眼<note place="inline">團</note>、刪
